{"article_id":"pvNizHTMoAK3yFGb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump says","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"the US military is `` locked and loaded ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to deal with North Korea ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"ramping up the rhetorical brinkmanship .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"`` Military solutions are now fully in place ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"locked and loaded ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"should North Korea act unwisely .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Hopefully Kim Jong-un will find another path ! ''","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"He spoke","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"as Pyongyang accused him of `` driving '' the Korean peninsula to the `` brink of a nuclear war '' .","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"North Korea has announced plans","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"to fire missiles near the US territory of Guam .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"The Pacific island 's homeland security agency issued a fact sheet on Friday with tips","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"for residents","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to prepare for any missile threat .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"It states :","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"`` Do not look at the flash or fireball","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"- it can blind you . ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` Lie flat on the ground","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and cover your head .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"If the explosion is some distance away ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"it could take 30 seconds or more for the blast wave to hit . ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Moscow said","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"the exchange of threats between Washington and Pyongyang `` worry us very much '' .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Foreign Minister Sergei Lavrov rated the risk of military conflict as `` very high ''","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"as he put forward a joint Russian-Chinese plan","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to defuse the crisis .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"German Chancellor Angela Merkel said","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"there was no military solution ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"and `` an escalation of the rhetoric is the wrong answer . ''","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"But later on Friday , at his private golf club in New Jersey , Mr Trump issued further threats to Pyongyang .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Asked about his `` locked and loaded '' tweet ,","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"he told reporters :","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"`` I hope","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that they","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"[ North Korea ]","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"are going to fully understand the gravity of what I said ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"and what I said is what I mean...","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"those words are very , very easy to understand . ''","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` If he","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"[ Kim Jong-un ]","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"utters one threat in the form of an overt threat","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"- which , by the way , he has been uttering for years ,","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"and his family has been uttering for years -","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"or if he does anything with respect to Guam or anyplace else","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"that 's an American territory or an American ally","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"he will truly regret it","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"and he will regret it fast . ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Mr Trump 's latest remarks follow his threat earlier this week","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to rain `` fire and fury '' on Pyongyang .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"His latest post came","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"hours after his Defence Secretary Jim Mattis attempted to cool tensions","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"by emphasising a peaceful resolution to the crisis .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Speaking in California late on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"the Pentagon chief said","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"it was his job to be ready for conflict .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"But he said","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"the effort by Secretary of State Rex Tillerson and UN Ambassador Nikki Haley `` has diplomatic traction ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"it is gaining diplomatic results '' .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Mr Mattis added :","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` The tragedy of war is well enough known .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"It does n't need another characterisation beyond the fact","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that it would be catastrophic . ''","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"When asked about US military plans for a potential conflict ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"the country was ready ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"but he would not `` tell the enemy in advance what I 'm going to do '' .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Also on Friday , North Korea 's official KCNA news agency accused Washington of a `` criminal attempt","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"to impose nuclear disaster upon the Korean nation '' .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Pyongyang 's media outlet said","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"America was making `` desperate efforts ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to test weapons in the Korean peninsula .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"The US is `` the mastermind of nuclear threat , the heinous nuclear war fanatic '' ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the report said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Despite the rhetoric from both sides ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"the Trump administration has been conducting behind-the-scenes diplomacy with North Korea for several months ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"the Associated Press news agency reports .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Washington has been addressing the issue of Americans","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"detained in the country","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"and escalating tensions on the peninsula ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"according to AP .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Joseph Yun , the US envoy for North Korea , and Pak Song-Il , a senior North Korean diplomat at the UN , are said to be leading the talks .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Tensions have risen","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"since North Korea tested two intercontinental ballistic missiles in July .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The regime was further angered by last week 's UN decision","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"to increase economic sanctions against it .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"North Korea said","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"it was finalising a plan","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"to fire medium-to-long-range rockets towards Guam ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"where US strategic bombers are based , along with more than 160,000 US citizens .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"There has been no indication","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"that any actual attack on the Pacific island is imminent .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"On Thursday Mr Trump suggested","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that his own statements on North Korea had not been tough enough ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"warning the regime to be `` very , very nervous '' .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"However , he added","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that the US would always consider negotiations .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"He also chided the North 's closest ally , China ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"it could do `` a lot more '' .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"China 's state-run Global Times newspaper wrote","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"that Beijing should stay neutral","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"if North Korea launches an attack","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"that threatens the US .","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"But it also said","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"if the US and South Korea attacked North Korea","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"to force regime change ,","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"then China must intervene","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"to prevent it .","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"Meanwhile , Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull said","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"his nation would be prepared to join a conflict against North Korea","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"if the US came under attack .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Australia would honour its commitment under a 1951 treaty ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"`` as America would come to our aid","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"if we were attacked '' .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Get news from the BBC in your inbox , each weekday morning","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":239,"left":238,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":130,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":123,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":127,"right":128,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":6,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":141,"right":236,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":131,"right":140,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":133,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":13,"right":132,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":14,"right":15,"re